{"tid":290412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做咩要成日鬧交","createTime":"2017-06-19T17:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T13:35:30.000Z","uid":113924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ef23d88554f168f7e0acb0a74f6e06524e5b13","tid":290412,"uid":113924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"話說拍拖三年，年紀唔細都想拉埋<br />\n但同條女成日鬧交<br />\n之前已經好左一排，又嘈<br />\n今次鬧交我都講到明我地可唔可以討論翻件事，點知佢又黎料<br />\n佢之前話我講野有時唔理人感受個d 我都盡量改，改到佢話見到我有改善<br />\n但佢個d 我真係未見佢改過<br />\n例如一走了之，翻舊賬，比男人要面子，不道歉不認低威<br />\n佢唔係港女的性格，唔拜金唔收兵唔臭雞，有時仲對我幾好<br />\n但一到吵就不得了，黎m 前個幾日我更加死得<br />\n點可以破局？散就短期內唔會，但好驚我對佢越黎越淡"},{"pid":"f972da45675a594e3430a14e748cbbfec265c80b","tid":290412,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d96ee8061193493f12b3143762cb888f0fe962","tid":290412,"uid":12823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:25:47.000Z","msg":"差d以為我男友開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56d0c4c67d662018f866cc148377ce1f6173859","tid":290412,"uid":94842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a6ea82920b6831e1f3f2889a9113a6417bdb2f","tid":290412,"uid":96979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實發你脾氣即係在乎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efaf30727b9a2f4e919917f2725c4dfc93b3be1","tid":290412,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實發你脾氣即係在乎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接講啦 其實係試緊條仔幾愛自己"},{"pid":"b49f7bb5b9c62a13b1a33dcd19508ffdb5ac4ed5","tid":290412,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實發你脾氣即係在乎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接講啦 其實係試緊條仔幾愛自己</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔係 我發佢脾氣佢唔開心我又會氹返佢<br />\n除非比我發現佢有第二個果啲"},{"pid":"2f88c68db377f521c270a4fd421f83e6b8dfc272","tid":290412,"uid":75421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:25:18.000Z","msg":"因為你真係唔理我感受囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb5e04e06fc548c9540a2dfe10979368ffa2b0a","tid":290412,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？"},{"pid":"47fb79467c5801a828f33fa1e5730ae95ef0ef53","tid":290412,"uid":113924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n有咩好講，佢地唔會明"},{"pid":"b7ea3fd31e48af857e3b5ba21e508eef99aca990","tid":290412,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T22:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n有咩好講，佢地唔會明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b30f02edf4608ba932db17b32bd1d1ef075bac","tid":290412,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T00:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a91b7206c9e3c6752965b3e26d68be2d66b8d83","tid":290412,"uid":113924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n有咩好講，佢地唔會明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又無理由將兩個人私人生活公諸於世<br />\n有時我想好好解決<br />\n但女人真係比情緒牽動得好緊要<br />\n你同佢講道理，佢會話你辯論<br />\n係佢眼中你講既所有野都有問題，但你話佢既野佢會耍太極咁耍走（個樣野的確係佢問題，我無屈佢）<br />\n當你唔理佢，佢可以冷過你<br />\n咁鬥落去有咩意思？<br />\n咁要面子同要強對段關係真係好？<br />\n禮拜頭因為一d 事嘈，到宜家都係冷戰mode<br />\n以前我會tum，但宜家不了"},{"pid":"9390b7d3be3d84526f561a130fb3c0b4e18ece06","tid":290412,"uid":54651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cdbb2816e38a688efdcb1d1559d97d9a905ccb","tid":290412,"uid":113924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪忍左佢 <br />\n如果你係想做人世既 忍忍讓讓少不免 <br />\n定係你認為佢一樣野都無忍你先 <br />\n既然係愛 就用愛解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係咁樣催眠自己<br />\n但當呢d 事越積越多<br />\n程度越黎越大，頻率越黎越多<br />\n你就開始懷疑係咪每次都係自己問題<br />\n愛係會令你著緊一段關係，然後認錯低頭<br />\n但當成為對方嘅習慣，就要諗下退路"},{"pid":"d07a9688a854b4d9fe07e9fe7e49544933b6e590","tid":290412,"uid":68864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n有咩好講，佢地唔會明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又無理由將兩個人私人生活公諸於世<br />\n有時我想好好解決<br />\n但女人真係比情緒牽動得好緊要<br />\n你同佢講道理，佢會話你辯論<br />\n係佢眼中你講既所有野都有問題，但你話佢既野佢會耍太極咁耍走（個樣野的確係佢問題，我無屈佢）<br />\n當你唔理佢，佢可以冷過你<br />\n咁鬥落去有咩意思？<br />\n咁要面子同要強對段關係真係好？<br />\n禮拜頭因為一d 事嘈，到宜家都係冷戰mode<br />\n以前我會tum，但宜家不了</blockquote><br />\n咁就算啦 邊個搵對方先就比人食住<br />\n幾愛都好 我都唔會咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310a1e26def021a948dadf46a0fb96eb5a254666","tid":290412,"uid":36131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打你同條女嘈交果陣會唔會同你啲朋友講？</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n有咩好講，佢地唔會明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又無理由將兩個人私人生活公諸於世<br />\n有時我想好好解決<br />\n但女人真係比情緒牽動得好緊要<br />\n你同佢講道理，佢會話你辯論<br />\n係佢眼中你講既所有野都有問題，但你話佢既野佢會耍太極咁耍走（個樣野的確係佢問題，我無屈佢）<br />\n當你唔理佢，佢可以冷過你<br />\n咁鬥落去有咩意思？<br />\n咁要面子同要強對段關係真係好？<br />\n禮拜頭因為一d 事嘈，到宜家都係冷戰mode<br />\n以前我會tum，但宜家不了</blockquote><br />\n咁就算啦 邊個搵對方先就比人食住<br />\n幾愛都好 我都唔會咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解愛個人都要咁多手段同心計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}